title: Rubrik Node Hardware Health: General Information
agents: Rubrik
catalog: hw/storagehw/Rubrik
license: GPLv3
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check shows the status of FRUS (field replaceable units) and disks as reported by the node.
 As long as "All FRUS in the node are healthy" and no disk errors are reported, the check will return "OK", else "CRIT".
 The check monitors the hardware health of individual Rubrik nodes including components and disks.
inventory:
 One service is created per node.